title: VA - Disco Vaults (A Dive Into Deep Rhythm) (2001)@flac
description:
Worth the search and high price! Warner Music (Greece) sent us their first installment of rare Disco tracks on double CD called Disco Vaults. 
The selection is outstanding and many appear here for the first time on CD. Taken from the Atlantic and Fantasy Records vaults this is a gem of a collection. Includes liner notes with scans of the original vinyl from which they were taken.
Please note that this is a limited release Greek import and a very difficult to obtain. (discomusic.com)
